# Guard for build-tarball's conditional patch application.
# Format: [!]<relpath-in-tarball>:<grep -E regex>   (ALL lines must hold)
# A leading '!' negates (the pattern must NOT be present).
#
# 0008 gates the meshstor p2pdma-fixes feature (member-AND advertise). It only
# applies when that feature is composed into the tree (meshstor-main), i.e. when
# the raid1_can_advertise_p2pdma() helper is present. On bare upstream `master`
# the helper is absent and 0009 handles upstream's raw P2PDMA assignment instead.
raid1-10.c:raid1_can_advertise_p2pdma
